      <body>
         <div>
            <head>Translated parts</head>
            <p xml:id="CH2a1530-start">
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:12:35.093+09:00">In Lǔ there was someone who was entering the city gate with a long pole,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:12:54.704+09:00">and first he held it upright,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:13:07.71+09:00">but it was impossible to get in;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:13:16.862+09:00">the he held it sidewise,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:13:40.404+09:00">but it was also impossible to get in.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:14:05.464+09:00">He was unable to come up with any efficient plan.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:14:27.102+09:00">Suddenly there was an old man who came up</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:14:29.311+09:00">and he said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:14:39.911+09:00">"I am not a sage,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:15:29.446+09:00">the only thing is that the things I have seen in my time are many.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-22a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T03:16:48.897+09:00">Why don't you saw over the middle of the pole and take then in separately?"</seg>
            <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:08:47.553+09:00">A southerner from Wu cam to the capital in the north</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:09:28.717+09:00">and was served a meal of yoghurt paste.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:09:53.525+09:00">He had no idea what this thing was</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:10:08.638+09:00">but forced himself to eat it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:11:21.955+09:00">On his way home he vomited and felt desperately sick.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:11:34.541+09:00">He told his son:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:12:07.669+09:00">"If I were to die together with these bastards</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:15:26.289+09:00">I would surely not have minded.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1530_CHANT_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-10-31T19:18:45.923+09:00">But one really ought to be careful with these people (who seem not to die of this awful stuff)!</seg>
                </p>
         </div>
